Package com.morpheusdata.model

Class VirtualImage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.morpheusdata.model.MorpheusModel
      • com.morpheusdata.model.projection.VirtualImageIdentityProjection
        • com.morpheusdata.model.VirtualImage
  • public class VirtualImage
extends VirtualImageIdentityProjection
    Describes a pre-built system image. The CloudProvider can be configured to sync existing images between your cloud provider and Morpheus.
